They all scattered
Ain’t no more Neptunes so P’s Saturn
Off the first ski up, they re-up
It’s a pattern
Like middle men they killing them
You know what happened
Ski

So be it

Lucky I ain’t TMZ it
So be it, so be it

snippet.title: Season 17: Powered Up! Official Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Prepare for a power surge in Season 17: Powered Up!

Sigma, Zenyatta, and Junkrat are joining the Stadium roster! Alongside them are 2 new maps - Esperança and Samoa, and the new Stadium Forge tool that lets you create, save, and share your builds like never before.

For the first time ever, both the Mythic Horang D.Va Hero Skin and Mythic Steel Death Reaper Weapon Skin are dropping at launch! Go wild in style or wield something sinister when you conquer the Premium Battle Pass and unlock up to 80 Mythic Prisms.

And that’s not all the Premium Battle Pass has to offer! Go from high school to high scores with the new Overwatch Academy and 8-Bit Legendary Skins, perfect for any playstyle.

Season 17 is also bringing Map Voting to Quick Play and Competitive, and the vibrant new Flashpoint map, Aatlis! In addition to a new Flashpoint map comes reworked versions of New Junk City and Suravasa, arriving mid Season 17.

And we’ve only scratched the surface! Dive into our limited-time 8-Bit game mode full of chaos and constant surprises, check out brand new skins coming to the Shop, and tons more you won’t want to miss.

Supercharge your fight when Season 17: Powered Up! launches on Jun 24.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

_
Follow #Overwatch2 for the latest news:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playoverwatch

Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/playoverwatch

Only one man has the particular set of skills... to lead Police Squad and save the world! Lt. Frank Drebin Jr. (Liam Neeson) follows in his father's footsteps in THE NAKED GUN, directed by Akiva Schaffer (Saturday Night Live, Popstar: Never Stop Never Stopping) and from producer Seth MacFarlane (Ted, Family Guy). Get a copy of What If? 2 and Randall’s other books at: https://xkcd.com/books
More serious answers to absurd questions at: https://what-if.xkcd.com/

This question comes from David, who asks: what would happen if one tried to funnel Niagara Falls through a straw?


Credits
*******
Randall Munroe | Narrator
Henry Reich | Writer & Director 
Lizah van der Aart | Illustration and Video Editing
Ever Salazar | Chief Chaos Controller
Know Art Studios | Music & Sound Effects

What If? The Video Series is the official adaptation of the What If? books by Randall Munroe and is produced by Neptune Studios LLC. 

Randall Munroe is the author of the New York Times bestsellers What If? 2, How To, What If?, and Thing Explainer; the science question-and-answer blog What If?; and the popular web comic xkcd (https://xkcd.com). A former NASA roboticist, he left the agency in 2006 to draw comics on the internet full time.

Henry Reich is the creator of MinutePhysics and executive producer of MinuteEarth and MinuteFood and founder of Neptune Studios LLC (the parent company for all three youtube channels).

snippet.title: 'Grey's Anatomy's' Eric Dane says he has 'one functioning arm' after ALS diagnosis in new interview
snippet.description:
The “Grey’s Anatomy” and “Euphoria” star tells ABC News’ Diane Sawyer about the moment he received his diagnosis about the incurable disease and how the symptoms have progressed.

He is speaking out for the first time in a television interview about his battle with ALS, a degenerative neurological disorder.

"I wake up every day and I'm immediately reminded that this is happening," Dane, 52, said in an interview with Diane Sawyer that aired Monday on "Good Morning America." "It's not a dream."

Just a few months after first revealing his ALS diagnosis publicly in April, Dane said he has lost function of his right arm and worries about what's next.

snippet.title: ALI SIDDIQ: RUGGED [Full Stand Up Comedy Special]
snippet.description:
Ali Siddiq is many things—a master storyteller, a comedy powerhouse—but a handyman?  Not even close. In his brand-new special, RUGGED, Ali trades the past gripping tales of his Domino Effect series (40+ million views on YouTube!) for a hilarious deep dive into his current home life, where his DIY attempts go horribly wrong.  From botched repairs and general home maintenance failures, to a family that has zero faith in his handyman skills, Ali delivers his signature blend of sharp wit and real-life storytelling. You’re going to laugh, cringe, and feel a little better about your own abilities.

Use iconic local businesses to funnel dirty cash into your criminal network in Money Fronts, today’s new update to GTA Online.

The head of San Andreas’ biggest money laundering network has heard about you, and it's time to form a mutually beneficial connection. Conspire with the very powerful — and very private — Mr. Faber and his sharply dressed consigliere Raf De Angelis to bring financial sophistication to your criminal enterprise.

snippet.title: [#WSWF] 메가 크루 미션 글로벌 대중 평가 | MOTIV(모티브)
snippet.description:
[#WSWF] 메가 크루 미션 글로벌 대중 평가 | MOTIV(모티브)

■ About MEGA CREW Mission Video

-타이틀: 위 더 피플 (We The People)
-총괄 디렉터: 말리

-작품 콘셉트
비판과 축제, 성찰이 강렬히 융합된 작품. 미국의 복잡한 정체성을 탐구하며 미국을 가장 진실되게 투영하는 건 분열된 국가에서 다양성을 유지하는 우리라는 것을 상기시킨다.

-하이 앵글 구간 연출 의도
각 안무의 대비감을 표현하고 빨강-하양의 대비로 긴장감 강조 및 분열의 심화를 암시한다.

-Title of Piece: We The People
-Executive Director: Marlee

-Concept of Piece
"We The People," is a powerful fusion of critique, celebration, and reflection. The piece explores the complexities of American society and reminds us that in a divided nation, we, in all our diversity, are the most honest reflection of this country.

-Directorial Intent for High-angle Section
Contrasting choreography roles and red-and-white color blocking were used to emphasize tension and hint at a lifting divide.

-作品タイトル: ウィー・ザ・ピープル (We The People) 
-チーフディレクター: マーリー

-作品コンセプト
批判とお祝い、そして内省が混ざり合った強力な融合作品。アメリカという複雑なアイデンティティを掘り下げ、分断が進む国で多様性を持ち続ける私たちこそ、この国を最も真に映す存在であることを改めて認識させる。

-ハイアングル演出意図 
各振付のコントラストを表現し、赤・白という色のコントラストで緊張感の高まりを強調し、分断の深刻化を暗示する。

==
국가의 이름을 걸고 전 세계를 무대로 완성한
거대 스케일의 퍼포먼스 전쟁 '메가 크루 미션'

새롭게 적용된 심사 포인트를 확인하고
당신의 마음을 움직인 크루에게 지금 바로 '좋아요'와 '댓글'로 응원해 주세요🔥

📍투표 기간: ~ 6/22(일) 18:00 (KST)
📍심사 포인트
① 하이 앵글 챌린지 구간
② 자국의 고유한 아이덴티티
③ 메가 퍼포먼스 디렉터 역량
📍유의사항
① 글로벌 대중 평가 점수는 유튜브 The CHOOM 채널에 게시된 글로벌 대중 평가 영상의 ''좋아요''수 x 100과 조회수의 합으로 산정됩니다.
② 동영상 캠페인 프로모션 및 각종 어뷰징으로 인한 조회수는 집계에 미포함 됩니다.

전 세계 쎈 언니들의 자존심을 건 글로벌 춤 싸움
〈월드 오브 스트릿 우먼 파이터〉
매주 화요일 밤 10시 본 방송

-
'MEGA CREW MISSION', The performance of great scale,
Completing for the whole world on behalf of the country

Check out new evaluation points
And support the team, which touched your heart, with 'likes' and 'comments'🔥

📍Voting Period : ~ 6/22(Sun)18:00 (KST)
📍Evaluation Point
① High Angle Challenge Part
② Unique National Identity
③ Mega Performance Director's Competence
📍Precautions
① The Global Public Rating will be calculated as the sum of ‘Like’ number x 100 and the hits of the global public rating video posted on the YouTube The CHOOM Channel.
② Video Campaign Promotions and other videos are not included.

A World Dance Battle of Unapologetic Women
〈WORLD OF STREET WOMAN FIGHTER〉
New episodes every Tuesday at 10 PM (KST)

-
国の名を背負い、世界を舞台として繰り広げられる
壮大なスケールのパフォーマンスバトル「メガクルーミッション」

新たに追加された評価ポイントを確認し、
あなたの心を動かしたクルーに今すぐ「いいね」とコメントで応援を送ってください🔥

📍投票期間: ~ 6/22(日) 18:00 (KST) まで
📍評価ポイント
① ハイアングルチャレンジのパート
② 自国のユニークなアイデンティティ
③ メガパフォーマンスのディレクターとしてのスキル
📍注意事項
① グローバル大衆評価の点数は、YouTube「The CHOOM」チャンネルに投稿されたグローバル評価映像の「いいね数 × 100 + 再生回数」によって算出されます。
② 動画キャンペーンや不正再生などによる数値は集計対象外となります。

世界中の“誇り高き女性”たちがプライドを懸けたグローバルダンスバトル
〈ワールド・オブ・ストリート・ウーマン・ファイター〉
毎週(火)夜10時本放送
